title: Circle Watch Face
summary: Very simple watch face with clean interface!
description: Tired of watch faces filled with functions that are not needed? Then you need this! This is very simple watch face with nice rotating circle for the seconds. Watch face supports round and square watches. Ambient mode included! You can change watch face theme to white in watch face settings. Also you can change watch face seconds accent color in the settings.
